Dialogs.Dialog: Do girls like to write some poems when they're in love？
Nene
Eh！？
What's the matter？
Ah, no. It's nothing... I don't think I'd do something like that...
I see...
I don't do it, okay？
When you wear a thin blouse, it's easy to see through it.
Nene
...Geez. What are you saying all of a sudden？
Well... I'm just thinking that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ should be careful with it.
What？ You want to monopolize me？
That's not what I meant...
Hehe. I'll be careful.
If humans have tails, where do you think the tails will grow from...？
Nene
What is this？
Will the tails grow out from here...？ Or here...？
Huh？ What are you doing？
Ah... Hahaha. I didn't do anything.
...Fishnet stockings...
Nene
What's wrong？ ...You look tired.
Ah, Teacher... No. I mean ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. It's nothing.
If so, that's good. Just don't mumble something like "fishnet stockings" to yourself. People will think you're a pervert.
...I'll be careful.
Ah, Nene-sama.
Nene
Eh！？ W-Why did you call me like that？
Ah... I don't know... Hahaha.
Geez. Don't deceive me with that laugh. ...Hehe, but you're cute, so I can forgive you.
(The mischievous ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was also cute...)
Nene
Hehe... Hot spring is nice, right？
Yesterday, I tried some hot spring bath set when I took a bath. I could feel that it was different from normal bath.
Yeah, and you were so pretty...
Huh？ What did you just say？
No. I mean if you use it often, your skin will become so pretty. Hahaha.
Nene
Hey, you got a moment？
What's wrong？
Just stand still for me, okay...？
W-Whoa！ What are you doing with my neck！？
Your collar is a mess, so I fixed it for you. Why do you get flustered like that？ Hehe.
Ah, thank you... Hah... I was scared...
Nene
Hey, do you think I've gained weight...？
Not at all！ That's not how you look to me.
Really？ Then that's good.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is always young and slim！
...？ Thanks...
Nene
What's wrong？ Why do you look so serious？
Is there a place you want to go？ Or something you want to eat？ Or...
...Hehe. What is this all of a sudden？
Is there anything that you're not happy about me...？
Geez. Just having you with me like this is more than enough, okay？
Nene
...*cough*
What's wrong？ Are you having a cold？ Do you want me to nurse you！？
Eh？ No, I'm fine. My throat just felt a little itchy... Ah, do you really want to nurse me？
Yeah, I can feed you some grated apple too.
Geez. I'm not a kid anymore.
Nene
Ah, you're right here.
Eh？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Is there anything you want？
I don't want anything, but... Hey, you know what day it is today, right？ I hope I'm not bothering you...
Ah, a chocolate？ Thanks！
I did something wrong when I made it... Sorry if it doesn't taste good.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ made it for me. I'm sure that it'll taste good.
I said I did something wrong. It's edible, but I don't have any confidence that you'd like it.
No way. If ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ made it, I'm sure that it'll taste good！
Hey, stop teasing me... But, you made me happy. Hehe. Thanks.
Nene
Ah, you're here. Come on... Did you forget what today is？
Eh？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What's the matter？
...Hmm. So, you really forgot about it.
Well...？
I'm looking for a person who will take my homemade chocolate. I don't know if I got the wrong guy here...
Today's Valentine's Day！ Sorry. I just realized it！
You don't have to force yourself to take it. I think there might be someone else who wants this.
Please！ I'm sorry. Please give it to me！
Hehe, for such a boyfriend who obediently apologizes to me... Here's your reward.
Nene
Ah, I found you！ Hey, I've been looking for you.
Eh？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What's the matter？
I have this special chocolate for a cute boy. What should I do with it？
Ah, today is Valentine's Day. Thank you, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
But before I give this to you... Confess now. Did you receive any chocolates from other girls before this one？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. I didn't even realize about it until I met you.
...Then you only got just one chocolate this year, from me, right？
Yeah, that's right...
Then... Ahem... Thank you for always staying by my side. Can you accept my love-filled chocolate？
Yes. Thank you, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. I'm very happy.
Nene
Ah, that boy right there. Wait a minute.
That boy？ Me？
Hey, come on... Here's your chocolate.
For Valentine's Day！？
I just give this out of obligation, so you don't have to concern about it so much.
But, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ gave it to me. I'm happy.
Hehe. If you're that happy, I'm very glad too. Ah... Don't tell me that you love eating sweets.
Well, sort of...
If you like it, just tell me. I can use it for reference next time. Hehe.
Okay... Eh？ Next time？
Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Hey！
Nene
Ah, what's up？
ell, today is White Day. So, I have a Valentine's Day's return gift for you.
Wow... Ah, but did you overdo it？ Is this okay？
Don't worry about that. Just open it.
Wow... Is it really okay for me to take this？ I'm happy...
(She seems to be extremely happy with it.)
Thanks. I'll take care of it.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
Well... It's the feeling that matters... Thanks.
(She didn't seem to like it that much...)
Now, I'm very impressed that you even gave me a return gift.
Impressed...？ This is not such a big deal, really.
But you must've put some effort into choosing this for me, right？ Thinking about that makes me happy. ...Is it weird？
It's not weird... But it makes me feel a little awkward.
But for me... Hehe, I wonder if you'll still feel awkward next year.
Are we talking about next year already？
Because this only happens once a year, right？ Hah... What kind of chocolate shall I make next year？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Hey！
Nene
Ah, what's up？
Today is White Day, so I have this Valentine's Day's return gift for you.
Hehe. If you want to give it to me that much, I should take it, right？
Yes, I really want to give it to you. Come on. Open it.
Wow, wonderful... Hehe. You really know my taste. This is a little unexpected.
(She seems to be extremely happy with it.)
Not so bad, I think. Hehe.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...I'll take it then.
(She didn't seem to like it that much...)
Is it bad that I even take a return gift from you...？
Don't worry about that. I was really happy when I got a chocolate from you.
Hehe. Thanks. Then I'll make a bigger chocolate for you next year. You'd better be prepared.
Bigger...？
Yes. And then I can expect something big as a return gift too, right？
Well... I'll try my best.
Hehe. Just kidding. Just your feeling is more than enough for me, okay？
Okay... Then next year, I'll try to find a return gift that is not too impossible to afford.
Ah, there you are. Hey, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Nene
Ah, you got some business with me？ Hehe. I wonder if it's what I'm thinking.
I guess it is... Here you go. Your White Day present.
Yay, thanks！ I've been looking forward to it. Really.
Open it. I'm not sure if you'd like it or not.
Wow... Thanks！ Did you read my mind when you chose this？
(She seems extremely happy to get it.)
Ah... You chose this for me. Hehe. Thanks.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Okay, thanks.
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
I thought that you might forget about White Day...
How could I forget it？
Hah... I can't use the punishment combo that I've prepared then.
Punishment combo...？
It'd be better if you really forgot about White Day！
Now you scared me...
Hehe. I wish you'd forget. That way, I could make you do a lot of things to make up for it.
Haha！ You face is all red. Hehe. So cute...
Well... Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. You're here.
Nene
Eh？ What's up？
Well, today is White Day, so... Here's your present.
Wow, thanks. Hehe. Can I open it now？
Of course.
Wonderful... I didn't expect that I would get this as a return gift.
(She seems extremely happy to get it.)
Hehe. Such a wonderful gift. Thanks.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Huh？ Thanks.
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
But... You didn't have to give me this return gift. Did I make you feel bad about this？
Not at all.
But, what I gave you was just a chocolate.
But, that chocolate was filled with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s love...
Eh？ My... love？
Ah... Did I say something weird？
No, you didn't... I guess.
Okay？ That's fine then...
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Nene
What's wrong？ Somehow, you're...
No, nothing's wrong... By the way, I kind of forgot about today...
...I see. Never mind. I didn't expect to get anything back. I'm fine. It's just a one-way gift then...
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Nene
Ah... Hehe. What's wrong？ You looked panic the moment you saw me.
Um... You see... Today is... that...
Hmm... So, that's what you think about today, huh？ I get it now.
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Nene
Ah, what's wrong？ Why do you panic like that？
Um... Sorry！ I totally forgot that today is White Day...
I see... Fine then. Don't worry. I was just looking forward to it for nothing...
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Ah！ No way！ I forgot to prepare a present for White Day...)
Nene
What's wrong？
Um... Sorry！ I forgot to prepare White Day's gift！
Ah, I see. If that's the case, it can't be helped then. Don't worry about me... okay？
(I'm the most idiotic guy in the world！)
(Okay, today is the sports festival.)
The match is about to start. Somehow, I feel nervous.
Nene
Ah, you're here. We're in different school years, but we both must do our best.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Did you come here to cheer for me？
Hehe. I want to see you while you're participating in the events.
Okay, thanks... All right. I'll do my best！
Ah, but you must be careful and don't hurt yourself. If you get hurt, you must tell me.
It's okay. It's not like I'm going to do anything dangerous.
Okay... Do your best but don't overdo it, okay？
(Yeah！ Perfect！)
Nene
As I could expect from you. Hehe. Such great effort you made.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, it was because you were cheering for me.
You're saying something cute like that. Do you want me to pat your head？
N-No, I'm fine. Everyone's looking this way...
Hehe, so cute...
(I'm glad I've been working hard on this...)
(This is totally bad...)
Nene
It's a little unfortunate.
Sorry. Even though you were cheering for me...
No, you already tried your best, right？ I think that's good enough.
But... This is still regrettable.
Next time you can do better, right？ I'll keep cheering for you, okay？
(I should've practiced harder...)
(Well, today is the culture festival.)
Nene
Hey, I heard from my friends... Are you participating in the Most Handsome Man Contest？
Yeah... Even your friends heard about it, huh？
This is amazing. Such a surprise.
I'm a bit pressured. ...I think I'll fail to qualify in the very first round.
Why？ I think you have the quality to be the most handsome man.
Really？
Yeah, I can guarantee that.
Okay, now I think I'll just try my best.
Hehe. I'll be cheering for you, so you must do your best.
(I won the contest...)
Nene
Congratulations！ You really won the contest！
It was a fluke...
That's not true. I can tell you that you're absolutely handsome.
Hehe. Please continue being a wonderful man, okay？
(It's good that I always take care of my appearance.)
(The contest result was totally no good...)
Nene
This is regrettable... You were so close.
All the participants were much more handsome than me.
That's not true. For me, you are...
The judges probably have bad eyesight. Geez. They just couldn't see it...
(I should've paid more attention to my appearance.)
Hmm. This is exciting...
Nene
Merry Christmas. Tonight is such a wonderful night.
Merry Christmas. It's nice to celebrate this occasion with everyone here.
Yeah. It's nice to have something like this occasionally.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s dress is really nice. It makes you look mature and feminine.
No, geez... Don't tease me.
Well... I have a Christmas present for you...
Thanks. I also have a present for you.
Then shall we exchange them？
Okay...
Wow... Wonderful... I'll never forget this year's Christmas for the rest of my life...
(She seems extremely happy to get it.)
Wow, thanks. I also like this.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
Well... Thanks. You really tried your best to pick this one for me, right？
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey, about my present...
Present？ You mean a present from Santa Claus？
Eh？ Ah... Never mind...
(Geez. I should've gotten something for her.)
Hey, you still have some time...？
Hmm？
Okay, I have to go home...
I see. Bye...
Hmm. This is exciting...
Nene
Merry Christmas. It's such a lively party, huh？
Merry Christmas. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you look good in that dress.
Eh？ Thanks. You really flattered me.
It's not flattery.
Hehe. Since today's Christmas, I'll take it as your honest opinion.
By the way, I have a present for you.
Really？ I also have a present for you.
Hehe, then let's exchange them.
Yeah...
Wow... Hehe, this is nice. Thanks. I'll treasure it.
(She seems to be extremely happy.)
Hehe. I think it's nice. Thanks. Somehow, you know what I like.
(I guess that's it.)
Hmm... Maybe you should try harder next time. I'm looking forward to next year's present.
(She doesn't look happy about it though...)
Ah, speaking of which... About the present！
Present？ I don't think Santa Claus will give me any...
Huh？
Geez, fine...
(Oh no. I should've gotten something for her.)
Can you accompany me after this？
I have to go home now. Bye...
I see. Bye...
Hmm. This is exciting...
Nene
Merry Christmas. It's such a magnificent party.
Merry Christmas... That dress really suits you well.
Hehe... You're flattering me all of a sudden. Do you want anything？
I'm not flattering you...
Thanks. Even though others also praised me, I wasn't as happy as when I heard your compliment.
Right. Are you ready to get a present from Santa Nene？
Thanks. I've also prepared to be Santa Claus myself.
Hehe. How about we exchange the presents？
Yeah...
Wow... To receive such a wonderful present from you... Yes, I'll treasure this all my life.
(She seems extremely happy to get it.)
Wonderful... Thanks. I'll treasure it.
(Well, I guess that's it.)
...Hehe. I probably have to wait until you're more mature, huh？
(She doesn't seem to like it that much...)
Hey, have you prepared to take the role of Santa Claus？
Haha. I'm too old to believe in Santa Claus.
...Geez, you idiot.
(Oh no. I should've gotten something for her.)
I still want to be with you. Will you accompany me a little longer？
Huh？
Ah, I have to go home... See you later.
I see. Bye...
Hmm. This is exciting...
Nene
Merry Christmas！ Are you enjoying the party？
Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... You look nice in that dress.
Eh？ Really？ This is a little embarrassing...
A serene holy night would be nice, but having fun in a party like this isn't bad.
Yeah.
You don't have anyone you want to spend your Christmas with？
No. I think it's not bad that I can spend time talking with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ like this.
Geez, that's sweet talking. Don't tease me. Take this！
(She treats me like a child again...)
Nene
Wow... Look. The Christmas tree is sparkling. It's beautiful...
When the lights are on, it gives totally different impression.
It's a little cold here, but I'm glad we've stayed here until it got dark... Achoo.
Are you cold？
Yeah, a little bit.
Let's go back or you might catch a cold.
No, I'm fine. I want to stay with you a little longer...
Are you really okay？
I'm fine. ...Ah, hey. Can you hold my hand？
Sure.
Thanks. Yeah, it's so warm... Hehehe.
Yeah... Somehow, I also feel warmer.
...Next year, let's do something like this again, okay？
Yeah, we'll do this again next year.
...How about the year after？
Of course. If it's okay with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, we'll keep doing this our whole life... Okay？
Eh？ Our whole life...
Yeah...
I'm... really happy to have you as my lover...
Yeah, me too...
Nene
Wow... Hehe, is it too soon for us to be at such a romantic place like this？
I wonder.
Hehe. So beautiful. For me, it would be like a dream if I could spend Christmas here with a wonderful guy.
A wonderful guy...
Dream and reality differ, huh？
...I know I'm not the perfect boyfriend for you and...
Hehe. What are you saying？ You are even more than perfect, you know？
More than I had ever imagined, you're such a cute, wonderful and reliable boyfriend...
That's... exaggeration...
Do you think I'm teasing you？ That's fine then. Hehe.
Well, I'll try my best to live up to your expectation.
Hehe, keep it up, keep it up. Let's keep it going for the next year.
And the year after that, and years after that.
Okay, I'll be looking forward to celebrate Christmas with my "most handsome boyfriend in the world" every year.
Nene
Look, look. The lights on the tree. So beautiful.
Hehe. What's the matter？
No, nothing...
I used to dream about celebrating Christmas with my boyfriend.
So, you're not quite happy to celebrate it with your not-so-dreamy boyfriend in the real world, huh...？
Hey, how could that be？ Hehe, what's wrong with you today？ You've been pouting like a kid.
That's because... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is very beautiful today...
...Um, thanks. But you're even more wonderful than the boyfriend in my dream, you know？
...Really？
Really. I had never imagined I could spend Christmas with such a lovely boyfriend like you.
And... I know that you will become an even more wonderful man in no time...
I will...？
Hehe, I guarantee. You will surely become a lovely, wonderful man.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, if you say so, I should have confidence in myself, right？
But... when you become such a wonderful guy, I wonder if the person beside you will still be me... Hmm？
That's a sure thing. I'm the one who has to beg you to always be with me.
...Hehe, thanks. Then shall we make a promise that we will always celebrate Christmas together from now on？
Sure, I promise. We will be together forever...
It's cold... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is not here yet.
Nene
Happy New Year.
Happy New Year, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Please be nice to me this year as well.
Okay, likewise. Please be nice to me.
Um, you look good in a kimono.
Hehe, thanks.
Then let's go for the shrine visit.
Okay... Are you done？
Nene
Yeah.
Hey, what did you wish for this year？
Most likely, the same as ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Eh！？ No way... For real？
Hmm？ Are you cold？ Your face is all red.
Ah, no... I'm not... I'm just... Geez...
Nene
Phew... It was really crowded.
Yeah. But we finally made it to pay respect to the shrine.
Hey, hey. If we properly pay a visit to the shrine on New Year's, everything will go smoothly this year, right？
What do you mean？
Um, well. For me, I prayed that I will also work hard this year, so please watch over me.
Hmm？ That's quite proactive.
Um, is it not the same for you？
For me, it's more like, "Please help me again this year."
Then let me make my wish with you this time.
With me！？
Yes. For this year, please continue being my nice partner.
Okay, likewise.
Nene
Then... see you later.
Ah, see you.
Hehe.
Huh？
Let's go together again.
Right. Next year, okay？
Okay. Bye-bye.
It's very hot today...
Nene
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry. Did I make you wait？
Not at all. By the way, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you really look good in a yukata.
Ah, thanks. Hehehe...
Then let's go to the shrine.
Nene
Wow, there are a lot more people than I expected.
Yeah. If we aren't careful, we might get separated from each other.
Wanna... hold hands？
Because... Come on. It'll be so much trouble if we get separated...
That's right. Okay.
Hehe. Grab my hand tightly so you won't get lost, okay？
Nene
Speaking of which, boys like masks, don't they？
Huh？ Ah, yeah. When I was a kid, my parents usually bought them for me.
Hehe. Then shall I buy one for you？
I'm fine. It's too embarrassing to wear one at this age.
It's a festival, after all. Come on. Let's choose matching masks, okay？
Nene
Wow... Beautiful.
Yeah, it's amazing... Eh？ Are you crying？ What's the matter？
Ah, sorry. It was so beautiful that I just started crying.
Are you okay？
Yeah. Let's come and watch it again next summer, okay？
Yeah. Let's come watch this again next year.
...Okay.
Ta~ma~ya~
Nene
Hehe. Hey, did you know that it's a paired word？
Yes. "Kagiya" is the other word, right？
Right, that's correct. "Tamaya" and "Kagiya" are the name of historic fireworks factories.
Then do you know which one was formed first？
Hmm, which one was it？
The answer is...
I don't know either.
Seriously？
Ah, look. The next ones are up.
Ka~gi~ya~
Nene
By the way, I used to join a test of courage with other kids in this town at this shrine when I was in junior high.
Huh？ Usually, the shrine wouldn't allow something like that.
The priest's brother happened to be the town mayor at that time. So, they had this planned up.
And you joined it？ Were you scared？
Very scared. I was sitting alone waiting for people to come.
...You were sitting alone？ Why？
Eh？ Because I was the ghost. If I didn't hide myself until people came so I could scare them, it would be meaningless.
Ah！ When you said you joined, you meant it like that！？
Yeah. And I was a haunted cat, so I had to put cat ears on.
(I want to see that.)
Nene
Urgh... This grilled squid really filled my stomach...
I should've stopped after the cotton candy and popcorn.
I told you so.
But it looked yummy...
And you still have half of the grilled squid left...
Ah, I can't eat anymore.
It's okay. Let me finish that half for you.
Okay... Here you go. Sorry.
Leave it to me.
You ate the same food yet you still can eat this. This is what men are made for, huh？
Nene
Thanks for walking me home.
I can't possibly let my girlfriend walk home alone at night.
Hehe. Then... see you.
Ah, see you later.
It's very hot today...
Nene
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry. Did I make you wait？
Not at all. By the way, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you really look good in a yukata.
Ah, thanks. Hehehe...
Then let's go to the Bay Bridge.
Nene
Wow... Beautiful.
Yeah, it's amazing... Eh？ Are you crying？ What's the matter？
Ah, sorry. It was so beautiful that I just started crying.
Are you okay？
Yeah. Let's come and watch it again next summer, okay？
Yeah. Let's come watch this again next year.
...Okay.
Ta~ma~ya~
Nene
Hehe. Hey, did you know that it's a paired word？
Yes. "Kagiya" is the other word, right？
Right, that's correct. "Tamaya" and "Kagiya" are the name of historic fireworks factories.
Then do you know which one was formed first？
Hmm, which one was it？
The answer is...
I don't know either.
Seriously？
Ah, look. The next ones are up.
Ka~gi~ya~
Nene
Thanks for walking me home.
I can't possibly let my girlfriend walk home alone at night.
Hehe. Then... see you.
Ah, see you later.
(Okay, the new semester starts today！)
Nene
Hehe, you're so pumped up.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Um... Please treat me well this semester, too.
Okay, likewise. With the new semester starting, you can't slack off on your job, okay？
Yes, okay.
(Okay, today is the closing ceremony！)
Nene
Hehe, seems like you really can't wait for the school break, huh？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Hahaha... Yeah.
But you can't keep playing around the whole break, okay？ You have to maintain your daily activities.
(Hmm, she always treats me like I'm a child...)
(I think the exam results have been announced...)
(I did perfectly for the exams this time.)
Nene
Ah, you're here. I saw the exam results. Your grades are so good that I was surprised.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... I was lucky that I guessed the right answers.
No, I know you really worked hard. Hehe.
(I think the exam results have been announced...)
(The result isn't too bad, but isn't good either... Quite mediocre.)
Nene
Ah, I saw the exam results. You did okay, huh？
Well, it's not too bad.
There were many things to do besides studying, huh？ But I know you could do better if you tried.
(Next time, I should try to study harder...)
(I think the exam results have been announced...)
(I did terribly for the exams...)
Nene
...It's quite unfortunate.
You saw the result... I'm ashamed.
It's not something to be ashamed of. The exams only measure your proficiency. Just try harder next time, okay？
(Hah... Next time, I want to show ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ how well I can do.)
Nene
Ah, you're here. You got a minute？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what's up？
Hey, today is your birthday, right？ So... Here you are.
A birthday present？
If you don't like it, please say so. I'll be more careful next time.
No way, it's something ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ picked for me. I'm definitely happy.
...Okay, thanks. But I want to know more about your taste, okay？
Okay... Thanks.
And another present.
Happy birthday.
...Yeah, thanks.
Nene
Ah, you're here. Geez, how cheeky you are to make me look for you.
Eh？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what's up？
Geez... Today is your birthday, right？ So... Here you go. Your present.
Thanks！
I was looking around the toy corner. But now I see that you've grown up, I should've picked something more suitable for you.
Toy corner...？
Hehe, I was kidding. I'm sure I picked the right thing for you.
Haha, thanks.
Well then...
Eh？
Happy birthday.
Yes... Thanks...
Nene
Ah, you're here. I've been looking for you.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what's up？
